	quests: [
		{
			dependencies: ["24174700F7FB771C"]
			description: [
				"To start our journey into the world of Mekanism Reactors, we'll start by making a &aFission Reactor&r. These are multiblock structures that generate massive amounts of heat by burning &3Fissile Fuel&r. This reactor does not produce power on its own, but the heat generated can be used to heat &bCoolant&r to be used to generate power in an &aIndustrial Turbine&r."
				""
				"The &aFission Reactor&r can be very dangerous, as a meltdown can cause an &cexplosion&r as well as &2Radiation&r spreading over a &o&b5 chunk radius&r, which lasts for several &nin-game weeks&r. "
				""
				"But we're going to be prepared for that. Let's make a &6Hazmat Suit&r, just in case."
			]
			id: "36B1995B495AA674"
			min_width: 350
			rewards: [{
				exclude_from_claim_all: true
				id: "49FE4FD579934237"
				table_id: 5236874501558129216L
				type: "random"
			}]
			tasks: [
				{
					id: "14BF9ADCB8F43ADC"
					item: "mekanism:hazmat_mask"
					type: "item"
				}
				{
					id: "0B06DCC5BA15895E"
