		{
			dependencies: ["1DE8B0C9A7195720"]
			description: [
				"The &6Fission Reactor&r needs &3Fissile Fuel&r to run. If you look up &3Fissile Fuel&r right now in &bJEI&r, I bet you'll get overwhelmed with everything you need to make it. It's okay, you've got this. Let's take it one step at a time."
				""
				"It all boils down to creating &eUranium Hexafluoride&r. To do this, let's focus on making these two gases: &bHydrofluoric Acid&r, and &eUranium Oxide&r."
