		{
			dependencies: ["3FFF9018DA2A2763"]
			description: [
				"Let's go through the checklist &b&oone more time&r to ensure we have everything ready to go before we boot it up:"
				""
				"1. &6Hazmat Suit&r On (Safety First!)"
				"2. &9Water/coolant&r pumping into an input Port."
				"3. &3Fissile Fuel&r pumping into an input Port."
				"4. A Port set to output the Heated Coolant, either to a trashcan or an &2Industrial Turbine&r."
				"5. A Port set to output &0Nuclear Waste&r leading to &eRadioactive Waste Barrels&r or machines to process it, or both!"
				""
				"If you're ready to go, hit that &eActivate&r button!"
				""
				"You can also adjust the &3Burn Rate&r to produce more &0Nuclear Waste&r, but start slow."
			]
