		{
			dependencies: ["6313B18820445882"]
			description: [
				"The &9Turbine Rotor&r is placed in the middle of the &6Turbine&r. For every &9Turbine Rotor&r, you will need &b&o2&r &aTurbine Blades&r. For this Turbine, we'll be using &b&o3&r &9Turbine Rotors&r."
