				""
				"You'll need to make a rectangular prism structure. The edges must be made out of &8Induction Casings&r. The faces can be made of either Casings, &aStructural Glass&r, or &eInduction Ports&r. It's best to have &b&o2 Ports&r: one for &9input&r, and one for &coutput&r. These can be changed using the &dConfigurator&r."
